('98921','34136','5','Modern detached house for sale with great sea views in Santa Ponsa'),
('98922','34137','5','Santa Ponsa is located in the southwest of Mallorca, only 16km from Palma. In just a few minutes drive from several golf courses, 3 marinas, supermarkets, restaurants and international schools.\r\nThis villa was built in the 90s on a 1.099m² plot. It be completely gutted in 2016 and renovated in modern style with high quality materials and the ultimate home automation. Completion will be autumn 2016th The villa offers on approximately 380m² of living space on the ground floor a living room, dining room with open modern fitted kitchen, utility room, bedroom with bathroom and dressing. On the 1st floor there are 3 more bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, some with terraces. From all floors you have a fantastic view of the bay of Santa Ponsa and the sea. A garage is available. High-quality facilities includes among others Dornbracht fittings, tiles by Philipp Stark, underfloor heating / heat pump, aluminum double glazed windows, control of home automation via iPad. A detailed list of features you can inquire\r\n'),
